Tuna Avocado Bowl

10 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbGluten Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch/Dinner

Tags:

QuickHealthyNo Cooking

Description

A fresh and nutritious bowl combining creamy avocado and protein-packed tuna, perfect for a light meal.

Ingredients

  • canned tuna: 1 can (5 oz)
  • ripe avocado: 1
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • lime: 1
  • fresh cilantro: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
